    <abstract id="aspace_9842b3692b5dfcecc41933a2c61596e1">This collection consists of diaries documenting the work and family life of Patrick Joseph Sullivan (1874-1944), a fuel inspector for the New York City Department of Education. The diaries date from 1905 to 1944.</abstract>
